metadata.description: The App logs information. Sensitive information should never be logged.

metadata.description: This App copies data to clipboard. Sensitive data should not be copied to clipboard as other applications can access it.
App uses SQLite Database and execute raw SQL query. Untrusted user input in raw SQL queries can cause SQL Injection. Also sensitive information should be encrypted and written to the database.

metadata.description: App creates temp file. Sensitive information should never be written into a temp file.

metadata.description: Files may contain hardcoded sensitive informations like usernames, passwords, keys etc.

playstore_details.title: Bitcoin Lightning Wallet TESTNET
playstore_details.description:
⚠️ TESTNET VERSION ⚠️

This lite SPV wallet fulfills Satoshi's Original Vision as witnessed here https://lists.linuxfoundation.org/pipermail/bitcoin-dev/2013-April/002417.html by implementing an off-chain payment layer known today as Lightning Network. 

In addition to being a digital gold Bitcoin now also becomes a cash which is suitable for small and frequent payments.

This approach allows for INFINITE scaling while not harming decentralization along the way since an off-chain Lightning payment has a zero footprint on a blockchain and thus block size and consequently a cost of running a full node may both remain low.
